          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Get a professional website without overpaying.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M22 16.92V19a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.86 19.86 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.86 19.86 0 0 1 3 4.18 2 2 0 0 1 5 2h2.09a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.12.86.3 1.7.54 2.5a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.41a16 16 0 0 0 6.5 6.5l1.08-1.09a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.8.24 1.64.42 2.5.54A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Responsive web design for cleaning services</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Your website works perfectly on mobile, tablet, and desktop.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-yellow-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-yellow-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Zap className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Reliable web design built for performance</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Fast-loading websites that improve user experience and SEO rankings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M3 21h18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
              <path d="M5 21V7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              <path d="M9 21v-6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              <path d="M8 9h.01M12 9h.01M16 9h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Complete web design and management services</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">We handle everything so you can focus on running your cleaning business.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
              <path d="M2 12h20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
              <path d="M12 2c3 3 4.5 6.5 4.5 10S15 19 12 22c-3-3-4.5-6.5-4.5-10S9 5 12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">SEO-optimized cleaning company web design</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Designed to rank on Google and attract local customers searching for cleaning services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-yellow-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-yellow-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Calendar className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Web design built to generate bookings</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Turn visitors into real clients with optimized layouts and calls-to-action.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Features Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-yellow-50 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background decoration -->
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-80 h-80 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-black">Features Every Cleaning Website Needs</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium">We build websites tailored for all types of cleaning services:</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-12 border border-yellow-100">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Carpet cleaning web design with booking forms</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Dedicated pages for carpet cleaning services with integrated booking systems</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Window cleaning web design with service pages</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Specialized pages showcasing window cleaning services and pricing</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">House cleaning website structure for local SEO</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Optimized structure to attract local house cleaning clients</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Dryer vent cleaning service pages optimized for search</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Specialized pages targeting dryer vent cleaning keywords</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Quote request forms to generate leads</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Easy-to-use forms that capture all essential service information</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Testimonials and reviews to build trust</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Show customer reviews and success stories to establish credibility</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Service area targeting for local clients</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Optimized to attract customers in your specific service locations</p>
